;AM-PM LOOKUP ROUTINE. FIRST CHARACTER MUST BE IN G.
;ACCEPTS ONE OF MORE LETTERS OF --     AND RETURNS + --
;	AM		1
;	PM		2
;	NOON		3
;	MIDNIGHT	4
;CLOBBERS B,D,E
;ONLY CALLED IN ONE PLACE; CODED AS A SUBR TO FACILITATE CHANGE SUCH
